.Dd $Mdocdate: September 07 2023 $
.Dt C_ARR_INIT 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm c_arr_init
.Nd initialize array
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb tertium
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In tertium/cpu.h
.In tertium/std.h
.Ft void
.Fn c_arr_init "ctype_arr *p" "char *s" "usize n"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn c_arr_init
function initializes the internal buffer of the array
.Fa p
to the buffer
.Fa s
of
.Fa n Ns \-1
bytes in size.
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Bd -literal -offset indent
ctype_arr arr;
char buf[64];
c_arr_init(&arr, buf, sizeof(buf));
.Ed
